name: Shoot Those Weird Birds in The Sky (Beta version)
name_original: Shoot Those Weird Birds in The Sky (Beta version)
description:
Welcome to a fun game, where you shoot weird birds... INFINITELY!  The level goes for an infinite amount of time, and obviously, your score will be saved!

Please note that this is a BETA version. There still might be some problems in the game. If there are any, please tell me via the comment section.
